{"tid":544519,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[數學分析] 教你用幾多成本（時間 & 金錢) 去溝女","createTime":"2018-01-29T15:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T15:26:33.000Z","uid":123335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"42c2be3caffcb5a0aba3cdf4ce4afda012eab97f","tid":544519,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T15:07:30.000Z","msg":"正所謂，「有女多野煩，冇女雖然自由但又寂寞」<br />\n但一般人都希望人生有個伴既，希望有真命天女<br />\n有女始終都會比單身好少少 <br />\n所以有女既benefits 會比單身大概有<strong><ins>1.5倍</ins></strong> <br />\n<br />\n而家陣自由主義盛行<br />\n偷食, ons , cheating , 綠帽 ... 盛行既時代<br />\n女朋友換畫既節奏，就黎快過保特跑100米<br />\n就算結左婚，都可以離婚，政府有晒數據顯示，離婚率已有逐年上升既跡象<br />\n更何況係男女朋友拍拖？<br />\n真係要預70% 拍得成落去, 30% 分手收場 <br />\n<br />\n我用kelly criterion 計左<br />\n大家應該要用幾多成本 (時間&amp;金錢) 於溝女身上 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Kelly criterion: </strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/d49930e9139de1c927cf12af7f475e9678a1f90d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikimedia.org%2Fapi%2Frest_v1%2Fmedia%2Fmath%2Frender%2Fsvg%2Fd49930e9139de1c927cf12af7f475e9678a1f90d&h=b9ddb8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nf* = [0.5(70/100)-(30/100)]/0.5<br />\nf* = <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10% </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以月入$15000 咁計 <br />\n每個月使 $1500 for 溝女就夠 <br />\n即係每星期使 $375 <br />\n<br />\n而時間每日24個鐘, 先減去8小時睡眠時間, 餘下16小時: <br />\n即係每日用1.6 小時 ，每星期就11.2 小時 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實諗諗下都好make sense <br />\n正常人大概每星期見女友2次 <br />\n每次使 $375 / 2 = $187.5 <br />\n約一次大概都要3.5 hr , 每星期約2次就 7hr <br />\n<br />\n每星期餘下: (11.2-7) hr = 4.2 hr <br />\n再將4.2hr / 7 = 0.6 hr = 36mins <br />\n<br />\n呢36 mins 就係每日你用黎覆gf d 無聊whatsapp 可以用既時間"},{"pid":"4ce4af54d33483c905df873177c0696ba479dd0a","tid":544519,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T15:08:21.000Z","msg":"Deeep"},{"pid":"0bda3e91b91ba7595546b833d24cdbe860b33acc","tid":544519,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T15:12: